{"tid":1689441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11.2 後 感 想 「2047」已經唔會有香港呢個名","createTime":"2019-11-02T20:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T20:29:51.000Z","uid":318271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b437cbfe9acd5a05483e8e69f1ef4eee092edd","tid":1689441,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:24:19.000Z","msg":"今日d post 都好負面，<br />\n不外乎：革命唔適合香港人、口號同行動完全唔一致、越來越少勇武、和理非未升格etc.<br />\n<br />\n其實，以上post絕對唔係分化撚，係事實，所以先咁多手足出post.<br />\n<br />\n只要係現場付出過既手足，無論「和」或「勇」今日一定深深體會到！無組織、無默契、東南西北無方向、大難臨頭各自走、最叻就係叫口號⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n其實之後究竟會變成點，無人知，但有一點大家一定知：退步左！<br />\n<br />\n當然一定有人出來吊我，插我，話我分化，不過我出呢個post係希望大家認清事實，作出調整，無論生理或心理都需要昇華。我希望香港人會勝利，更希望大家可以一齊走到終點，煲底相擁相認！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n堅持到底，就是勝利！"},{"pid":"22c1bf6f7d8aa496b2438e588a7bb6befdadc2a3","tid":1689441,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:24:47.000Z","msg":"自推，唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cf875b58c2982e15076e30da7b99bbfd2b8321","tid":1689441,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:25:02.000Z","msg":"自推，唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f85d856156d7dd85a8f5298133b3aa8f81743e3","tid":1689441,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:28:28.000Z","msg":"自推，唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41952189b8dc00d25ba80f87d5ddd4eab162f16b","tid":1689441,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:28:40.000Z","msg":"自推，唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3ae180c59b9cfccc991f40a08557142147681c","tid":1689441,"uid":318271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T20:28:52.000Z","msg":"自推，唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9497496a6f654ac9cc5